a	Municipal Accountant to record purchases of drugs and medicines, medical, dental and laboratory supplies, Agricultural & Marine Supplies, Animal/Zoological Supplies, Food Supplies, Office Supplies, Other Supplies & Materials to the appropriate inventory account and recognize expenses according to the SSMI for the fair presentation of balances in the financial statements;

